Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:49.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:53.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nexcept for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:03:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
