Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.69,0:03:09.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:16.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
